      "\n",
      "1. StandardScaler (sklearn):\n",
      "   - Fit sur train, transform sur test\n",
      "   - Resultat: mean=0, std=1\n",
      "\n",
      "2. Rolling Normalize:\n",
      "   - Pas de lookahead bias\n",
      "   - Utilise mean/std des N derniers jours\n",
      "\n",
      "3. Percentile Rank:\n",
      "   - Robuste aux outliers\n",
      "   - Resultat: [0, 1] = percentile actuel\n"
